      • ask

        public static boolean ask(java.lang.String question)
        Asks user if they want to proceed updating the field. The user types answers with "y" or "n" via keyboard.
        Parameters:
        question - - the question printed before reading from the keyboard
        Returns:
        true if the user wants to update the specified field (y) or false if the user doesn't want to update the specified field (n)
